    "type": "download",
    "link": "https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/downloads/world-down-syndrome-day-world-activity/",
    "title": {
      "rendered": "World Down Syndrome Day World Activity"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"791\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Globe-791x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-765\" srcset=\"https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Globe-791x1024.png 791w, https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Globe-232x300.png 232w, https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Globe-768x994.png 768w, https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Globe-1187x1536.png 1187w, https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Globe.png 1545w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 791px) 100vw, 791px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Get creative and celebrate <strong>World Down Syndrome Day</strong> with this <strong>fun and interactive globe coloring activity!</strong> 🌍</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kids can <strong>design their own unique globe</strong> to show their support and spread awareness. After coloring, they’ll <strong>cut, fold, and glue</strong> the pieces together to complete their globe creation!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>✨ <strong>What’s Included?</strong><br>✔️ Printable globe coloring page<br>✔️ Easy cut-and-paste assembly<br>✔️ Perfect for classrooms, homeschool, or family fun!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s celebrate differences in a colorful way! 💙💛</p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
    "excerpt": {
      "rendered": "<p>Get creative and celebrate World Down Syndrome Day with this fun and interactive globe coloring activity! 🌍 Kids can design their own unique globe to show their support and spread [&hellip;]</p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
