    "content": {
      "rendered": "\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"883\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-19-at-10.55.43 AM-883x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-761\" srcset=\"https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-19-at-10.55.43 AM-883x1024.png 883w, https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-19-at-10.55.43 AM-259x300.png 259w, https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-19-at-10.55.43 AM-768x890.png 768w, https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-19-at-10.55.43 AM-1325x1536.png 1325w, https://c9s.3d3.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-19-at-10.55.43 AM.png 1446w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 883px) 100vw, 883px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Get creative and celebrate <strong>World Down Syndrome Day</strong> with this <strong>fun and interactive sock coloring activity!</strong> 🎨🧦</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kids can <strong>design their own unique socks</strong> to show their support and spread awareness. After coloring, they’ll <strong>cut, fold, and glue</strong> the pieces together to complete their sock creation!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>✨ <strong>What’s Included?</strong><br>✔️ Printable sock coloring page<br>✔️ Easy cut-and-paste assembly<br>✔️ Perfect for classrooms, homeschool, or family fun!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s celebrate differences in a colorful way! 💙💛</p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
    "excerpt": {
      "rendered": "<p>Get creative and celebrate World Down Syndrome Day with this fun and interactive sock coloring activity! 🎨🧦 Kids can design their own unique socks to show their support and spread [&hellip;]</p>\n",
